Package Control Messages
========================

LaTeXTools
----------

  LaTeXTools Plugin version 3.12.6 (2016-11-06) changelog:
  
  Features:
  - Improved the error reports of the preview feature
  - The system check now also searches for packages used by the preview feature

  LaTeXTools Plugin version 3.12.5 (2016-11-03) changelog:
  
  Bugfixes:
  - Fix an error which disabled cwl completion (#910)
  - Improved the resolution if math-live preview (#901)
  - Improved the feedback if preview fails

  LaTeXTools Plugin version 3.12.4 (2016-11-02) changelog:
  
  Bugfixes:
  - Fix an error where Sumatra was being run hidden (#900)
  - Fix an issue which caused the Script builder to not run on OS X / macOS (#894)
  - Fix an error where copy_on_build setting was not actually being honored (#893)

  LaTeXTools Plugin version 3.12.3 (2016-11-01) changelog:
  
  Features:
  - Phantoms now use magick command if its available
  - Improved detection of Ghostscript
  
  Bugfixes:
  - Fixed a typo which caused convert not to properly work with included images
  - Fix extra \ introduced by CWL completions (#888)

  LaTeXTools Plugin version 3.12.2 (2016-11-01) changelog:
  
  Bugfixes:
  - Fixed a bug, which disabled forward sync

  LaTeXTools Plugin version 3.12.1 (2016-11-01) changelog:
  
  Features:
  - Added a command to check your system to have all required programs installed
  - Improved the sanity of calling external commands
